  "description": "Blend oscillating at mid-point with maximum interference — the engine cannot decide whether it is memory or perception. The interference modulates both channels simultaneously into a flickering identity crisis. Neither grain nor direct signal is stable. What emerges is a third thing: the moment of forgetting, sustained as music.",
